{"date":"2016-01-07","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/3b/95/149993_w0q6W.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/3b/95/149993_w0q6W.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/3b/95/149993_w0q6W.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/3b/95/149993_w0q6W.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/3b/95/149993_w0q6W.jpg"},"summary":"神奈川县，金泽百景。学生北条文太郎并没有“将来想要做什么”这种明确的梦想。怀着隐约的焦躁感，他与朋友们热闹地度过每一天。\r\n\r\n某天，文太郎被自己有些在意的异性同学黑田砂雪拜托，希望让他帮忙制作并发售美少女游戏。砂雪看到了文太郎为演剧部写的绝妙脚本，并因此相中了他。对于完全不了解美少女游戏的文太郎来说，这实在是不切实际。但，砂雪拥有能令事物实现、成功的力量和眼光。\r\n\r\n在尽是问题儿童的人才当中，游戏能成功地制作出来吗？能卖得出去吗？能得到些什么吗？年轻人们向着无尽的荒野迈出了脚步—— ","name":"少女たちは荒野を目指す","name_cn":"少女们向荒野进发","tags":[{"name":"2016年1月","count":349,"total_cont":0},{"name":"projectNo.9","count":255,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAL改","count":240,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":233,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改","count":202,"total_cont":0},{"name":"田中ロミオ","count":196,"total_cont":0},{"name":"少女们向荒野进发","count":146,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2016","count":117,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":102,"total_cont":0},{"name":"花泽香菜","count":96,"total_cont":0},{"name":"佐藤卓哉","count":66,"total_cont":0},{"name":"后宫","count":34,"total_cont":0},{"name":"松竜","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2016年一月番","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"业界","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2016年","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"千菅春香","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"綾奈ゆにこ","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"タカヒロ","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"花澤香菜","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山下誠一郎","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"励志","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改编","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"明坂聡美","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"project_No.9","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"石田彰","count":4,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"